   A backer of the cranberry muffin, Sen. Lloyd Kincaid, didn't
think much of the idea.
   ``I think it's an insult to the children who are backing the
cranberry muffin,'' said Kincaid, whose bill is before a Senate
committee.
   Wisconsin ranks second behind Massachusetts in the production of
cranberries.
  
