<FIRST>u f PM-Japan-Merger 1stLd-Writethru   08-29 0686</FIRST>
<SECOND>PM-Japan-Merger, 1st Ld-Writethru,0708</SECOND>
<HEAD>Merger of Two Japanese Banks Creates 2nd Largest Bank in World</HEAD>
<HEAD>EDS: SUBS lead to restructure; UPDATES with 3 grafs after 16th graf
`Analysts said that...' to ADD further comment by analysts. Picks up graf
17 pvs, `Japanese banks are...'</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By TETSUO JIMBO</BYLINE>
